# Product Requirements Document (PRD)

# HD Care Mobile API System

## AI-Based Hemodialysis Monitoring Platform

---

# 1. Product Overview

## Product Name

HD Care (DIALIFE)

---

## Product Description

HD Care adalah platform monitoring pasien Hemodialysis berbasis AI yang membantu pasien memonitor:

* asupan cairan
* makanan dan minuman
* nutrisi
* urine output
* keseimbangan cairan harian

Sistem menggunakan:

* Mobile App Flutter
* REST API Django
* AI Food & Urine Detection

---

# 2. Objective

Membangun backend API yang:

* ringan
* scalable
* realtime
* mudah diintegrasikan dengan Flutter
* mendukung AI inference

---

