# 4.2 KALKULATOR CAIRAN

## Tujuan

Menghitung batas cairan harian pasien HD.

---

# Formula

\mathrm{Daily\ Fluid\ Limit} = \mathrm{Urine\ Output} + 500\ \mathrm{ml}

---

# Input

* berat badan kering
* urine 24 jam

---

# API Endpoint

```text id="w6md0n"
/api/fluid/calculate/
```

---

# Request

```json id="lmz3kr"
{
  "dry_weight": 55,
  "urine_output_ml": 700
}
```

---

# Response

```json id="0m2c1n"
{
  "recommended_fluid_limit_ml": 1200,
  "status": "aman"
}
```

---

